17
00:03:01,900 --> 00:03:03,633
(Muscular Armteeth)
Dinner time.

18
00:03:03,766 --> 00:03:04,866
(On the full top of the Soul-building Stage)
Armteeth.

19
00:03:07,666 --> 00:03:09,933
