20
00:03:10,866 --> 00:03:13,200
It spares me the trouble of looking for you.

21
00:03:13,666 --> 00:03:16,300
It seems Meizi is still having fun in another area.

22
00:03:17,366 --> 00:03:18,333
Gentlemen,

23
00:03:19,233 --> 00:03:20,800
