(The Western Gobi Desert)

39
00:03:45,333 --> 00:03:52,633
(The Ease Sect's Sheng Liao
VS the Lingxiao Pavilion's Yue Tong)

40
00:03:52,633 --> 00:03:53,433
White Black.

41
00:03:54,866 --> 00:03:57,633
