62
00:05:10,533 --> 00:05:12,966
You and me, plus your mom and your sister.

63
00:05:13,066 --> 00:05:13,933
There are four of us.

64
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,000
Seriously?

65
00:05:16,566 --> 00:05:17,666
Anyway, in the competition,

66
00:05:18,733 --> 00:05:20,266
Scale in the Mature Stage

67
00:05:20,866 --> 00:05:22,866
