77
00:05:43,033 --> 00:05:44,266
From now on,

78
00:05:44,366 --> 00:05:46,133
if you can keep training

79
00:05:46,233 --> 00:05:48,266
and save some points of energy every day,

80
00:05:48,366 --> 00:05:50,533
