85
00:05:59,266 --> 00:06:00,800
How is it going with your energy saving?

86
00:06:01,366 --> 00:06:06,300
(Energy Deposit)

87
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:09,500
(Energy Deposit: Two)

88
00:06:10,833 --> 00:06:11,833
Sorry, Dad.

89
00:06:11,833 --> 00:06:13,700
I'll begin to train now!

90
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:18,433
Scale is an Emperor after all.

91
00:06:18,833 --> 00:06:19,866
It should be his match.

92
00:06:20,266 --> 00:06:21,966
Though Scale is an Emperor,

93
00:06:22,233 --> 00:06:23,366
