115
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,333
Just do it.

116
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,100
Be vigilant.

117
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:27,266
Presumptuous brats.

118
00:07:27,666 --> 00:07:30,333
Let me send you to the other world.

119
00:07:38,566 --> 00:07:39,166
That is...

120
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:41,366
Didn't you say you'd defeat me?

121
00:07:42,333 --> 00:07:43,466
(The Eastern Gobi Desert)
Then how can you die here?

122
00:07:44,266 --> 00:07:45,200
(The Ease Sect's Nie Xing)
Loong Nitian?

123
00:07:45,766 --> 00:07:46,966
(VS the World-shaking Super Invincible Temple's Long Nitian)
Loong Nitian.

124
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,966
You...

125
00:07:48,366 --> 00:07:49,733
Let me get rid of him first.

126
00:08:00,366 --> 00:08:02,100
A petty snake in the Mature Stage

127
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:04,500
