133
00:08:24,433 --> 00:08:25,966
After a week's intensive training,

134
00:08:26,433 --> 00:08:28,266
I saved 25 points of energy

135
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,600
which was

136
00:08:30,066 --> 00:08:31,100
all spent before.

137
00:08:32,333 --> 00:08:33,233
However,

138
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,933
