139
00:08:36,366 --> 00:08:37,466
We can't lose face.

140
00:08:38,366 --> 00:08:39,600
Use the forbidden skill.

141
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:40,733
Scale.

142
00:08:43,933 --> 00:08:45,100
Lend me ten points first.

143
00:08:56,733 --> 00:08:59,866
(Power Loan
The second special skill of Azure Scale Loong)

144
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:06,066
He has used that demonic forbidden skill in the end.

145
00:09:09,366 --> 00:09:10,300
Stupid centipede.

146
00:09:10,566 --> 00:09:12,100
I'll smash you.

147
00:09:12,566 --> 00:09:13,633
Idiot.

148
00:09:14,166 --> 00:09:15,066
Old man.

149
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:16,000
Is it still the era

150
00:09:16,100 --> 00:09:17,333
