151
00:09:17,533 --> 00:09:18,966
Time for you to retire.

152
00:09:23,933 --> 00:09:27,466
A child of flesh dares to be overbearing?

153
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:28,966
No.

154
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:30,533
I'm running out of energy.

155
00:09:35,166 --> 00:09:35,733
Look out!

156
00:09:36,033 --> 00:09:37,600
Die! Rascal.

157
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,233
Lend me ten more.

158
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:47,666
Excellent.

159
00:09:52,866 --> 00:09:55,100
Darn.

160
00:09:55,733 --> 00:09:57,533
Rascal.

161
00:09:58,066 --> 00:10:01,000
I must slaughter you today.

162
00:10:05,666 --> 00:10:06,233
Son.

163
00:10:06,666 --> 00:10:09,466
(Ribs Jail
Skill)

164
00:10:09,533 --> 00:10:10,266
Loong Nitian.

165
00:10:10,866 --> 00:10:11,566
Thorn Back.

166
00:10:15,966 --> 00:10:16,900
Stay away.

167
00:10:17,466 --> 00:10:18,800
You fool.

168
00:10:20,766 --> 00:10:21,366
Thorn Back.

169
00:10:23,933 --> 00:10:25,033
Rascal.

170
00:10:25,366 --> 00:10:26,800
Any last word?

171
00:10:27,266 --> 00:10:28,000
Crap.

172
00:10:28,333 --> 00:10:29,666
Whatever.

173
00:10:30,233 --> 00:10:30,866
Scale.

174
00:10:31,766 --> 00:10:32,866
Thirty points.

175
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:34,600
Son.

176
00:10:34,866 --> 00:10:37,000
You will have to pay high interest on that loan!

177
00:10:49,566 --> 00:10:51,400
Brat.

178
00:10:57,066 --> 00:10:58,000
Sky-whacking

179
00:10:58,400 --> 00:11:00,200
Punch!

180
00:11:01,833 --> 00:11:02,833
(The Eastern Gobi Desert
The Ease Sect's Nie Xing)

181
00:11:02,866 --> 00:11:05,900
(VS the World-shaking Super Invincible Temple's Long Nitian)

182
00:11:05,933 --> 00:11:09,133
(The Eastern Gobi Desert
The World-shaking Super Invincible Temple's Long Nitian)

183
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,933
(The Western Gobi Desert
The Ease Sect's Sheng Liao)

184
00:11:12,966 --> 00:11:14,700
(VS the Lingxiao Pavilion's Yue Tong)

185
00:11:14,700 --> 00:11:15,966
Little bear.

186
00:11:16,566 --> 00:11:17,933
Where are you?

187
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,433
No.

188
00:11:28,366 --> 00:11:30,233
We are not done yet.

189
00:11:33,733 --> 00:11:34,933
Or...

190
00:11:36,366 --> 00:11:37,633
You are hiding there!

191
00:11:55,166 --> 00:11:56,533
You are pretty tough.

192
00:11:58,033 --> 00:11:59,066
White Black.

193
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,800
Time to say farewell.

194
00:12:16,233 --> 00:12:16,833
Yue Tong.

195
00:12:17,566 --> 00:12:18,300
Have faith in yourself.

196
00:12:19,166 --> 00:12:20,700
You may be a better pet trainer

197
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,633
than I.

198
00:12:24,733 --> 00:12:26,466
Devour it, Armteeth.

199
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,133
White Black.

200
00:12:32,633 --> 00:12:35,333
Don't die.

201
00:12:35,366 --> 00:12:36,166
(Lords' Resonance)

202
00:12:38,666 --> 00:12:39,733
That mastering skill is so strong.

203
00:12:39,733 --> 00:12:40,866
It's a Lord's skill.

204
00:13:07,933 --> 00:13:08,733
(The Eastern Gobi Desert
The Ease Sect's Sheng Liao)

205
00:13:08,733 --> 00:13:09,466
(VS the Lingxiao Pavilion's Yue Tong)

206
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:17,166
(The Eastern Gobi Desert
The Lingxiao Pavilion's Yue Tong)

207
00:13:29,533 --> 00:13:30,800
I'm ridiculously strong.

208
00:13:31,366 --> 00:13:32,066
Loong Nitian.

209
00:13:34,666 --> 00:13:35,533
There he is.

210
00:13:38,066 --> 00:13:40,100
Hey. I got the bracelet first.

211
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:41,166
Don't you snatch it.

212
00:13:42,066 --> 00:13:43,633
Who wants that?

213
00:13:43,833 --> 00:13:44,933
I've come

214
00:13:45,266 --> 00:13:46,800
to thank you for saving me.

215
00:13:48,100 --> 00:13:49,800
Th... thank me?

216
00:13:52,333 --> 00:13:54,566
- Th... thank me? - Yes.

217
00:13:54,900 --> 00:13:56,033
Something wrong?

218
00:13:56,833 --> 00:13:57,933
I'm just showing my gratitude.

219
00:13:58,066 --> 00:13:59,100
Do you have to be like this?

220
00:13:59,566 --> 00:14:00,566
But I...

221
00:14:01,066 --> 00:14:04,266
I've borrowed 50 points of energy for my dignity

222
00:14:04,266 --> 00:14:05,733
which shall be paid off within a month

223
00:14:05,733 --> 00:14:07,266
as along with much interest.

224
00:14:07,366 --> 00:14:10,233
So I have to train crazily to pay my debt.

225
00:14:10,533 --> 00:14:13,600
It's so distressing to think about that.

226
00:14:15,966 --> 00:14:21,266
(The Grassland
The Ease Sect's Meizi VS the Lingxiao Pavilion's Jun Yunzi)

227
00:14:29,933 --> 00:14:31,600
What's the point of jumping here?

228
00:14:37,866 --> 00:14:38,566
(Fusing Transformation: Saber
Innate skill)

229
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:40,000
(Steelball
In the sixth phase of the Mature Stage)

230
00:14:43,300 --> 00:14:45,000
(The Grassland
The Ease Sect's Meizi VS the Lingxiao Pavilion's Jun Yunzi)

231
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:57,066
(The Grassland
The Lingxiao Pavilion's Jun Yunzi)

232
00:15:01,433 --> 00:15:02,000
Master Gu.

233
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,000
Are you all right?

234
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:04,233
Mister Liu.

235
00:15:04,700 --> 00:15:05,400
Mister Duan

236
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:06,633
