237
00:15:09,366 --> 00:15:10,000
Duan Ye.

238
00:15:10,033 --> 00:15:11,100
Why did you do that?

239
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:14,300
The bracelet?

240
00:15:14,900 --> 00:15:15,933
It's for you.

241
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:20,200
I...

242
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,600
will no longer work for the Rakshas Sect.

243
00:15:24,366 --> 00:15:26,066
So you are coming back?

244
00:15:26,566 --> 00:15:27,066
No.

245
00:15:27,666 --> 00:15:28,933
I will stay in the Rakshas Sect.

246
00:15:32,033 --> 00:15:33,066
Morons.

247
00:15:33,066 --> 00:15:35,200
How do I look into Master Fan's death if I leave the sect?

248
00:15:37,866 --> 00:15:38,766
I quit.

249
00:15:38,933 --> 00:15:40,000
Contact me later.

250
00:15:44,066 --> 00:15:44,766
Right.

251
00:15:51,433 --> 00:15:52,866
Good-for-nothings.

252
00:16:18,833 --> 00:16:20,700
Thank you so much.

253
00:16:20,866 --> 00:16:21,866
(Scarlet Evil Eye
In the top phase of the Soul-building Stage)

254
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:23,600
Gnats.

255
00:16:24,933 --> 00:16:26,733
Now, let me put an end

256
00:16:27,233 --> 00:16:30,300
to this boring competition.

257
00:16:32,533 --> 00:16:33,300
Oh, no.

258
00:16:35,366 --> 00:16:36,100
He missed?

259
00:16:38,033 --> 00:16:38,666
No.

260
00:16:38,700 --> 00:16:39,700
His target is...

261
00:16:41,666 --> 00:16:42,533
the turtle.

262
00:16:53,666 --> 00:16:55,000
What is it this time?

263
00:16:59,900 --> 00:17:00,566
No.

264
00:17:00,633 --> 00:17:02,133
The island has sunk so much in a second.

265
00:17:03,066 --> 00:17:03,666
Governor.

266
00:17:04,600 --> 00:17:06,266
That bastard of the Ease Sect.

267
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,333
Team Five, Six, Seven and Eight.

268
00:17:08,433 --> 00:17:09,200
Move out now.

269
00:17:09,533 --> 00:17:11,533
Save all the drowning candidates.

270
00:17:11,666 --> 00:17:12,366
Yes.

271
00:17:48,766 --> 00:17:49,866
Mister Liu.

272
00:17:59,600 --> 00:18:00,833
How dare he plot against us?

273
00:18:00,966 --> 00:18:02,266
If I still had any saved energy,

274
00:18:02,333 --> 00:18:03,900
