275
00:18:04,233 --> 00:18:05,133
Forget him.

276
00:18:05,500 --> 00:18:06,466
The bracelets are in water.

277
00:18:06,733 --> 00:18:08,033
We are going to be terminated.

278
00:18:09,433 --> 00:18:11,133
Scale, take me to the sky.

279
00:18:12,200 --> 00:18:13,266
Stop it.

280
00:18:13,333 --> 00:18:15,133
It can't even help itself.

281
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:17,866
Candidates, calm down.

282
00:18:18,066 --> 00:18:18,700
We are here.

283
00:18:26,366 --> 00:18:27,133
Chief Kuai.

284
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,433
Haven't you gone too far?

285
00:18:30,166 --> 00:18:32,600
Have I violated any rules?

286
00:18:32,966 --> 00:18:34,733
The Rakshas Sect is terminated.

287
00:18:35,033 --> 00:18:36,733
There are four teams left.

288
00:18:37,166 --> 00:18:39,266
The Miraculous Pivot Sect is terminated.

289
00:18:39,566 --> 00:18:41,466
There are three sects left.

290
00:18:42,100 --> 00:18:43,933
The Baimu Study is terminated.

291
00:18:44,100 --> 00:18:45,900
There are two teams left.

292
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:49,400
Stop wasting time, little girl,

293
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:52,033
and announce my victory.

294
00:18:57,333 --> 00:18:58,933
All examiners.

295
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,933
All examiners.

296
00:19:01,366 --> 00:19:02,933
The competition is not over yet.

297
00:19:03,100 --> 00:19:05,466
The remaining teams shall carry on.

298
00:19:05,466 --> 00:19:06,100
What?

299
00:19:07,933 --> 00:19:09,933
There are two teams left.

300
00:19:10,333 --> 00:19:11,766
The Beckon Society of the Ease Sect

301
00:19:11,866 --> 00:19:12,700
and

302
00:19:14,566 --> 00:19:15,733
the Lingxiao Pavilion.

303
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:24,033
(The All-devouring Whale: The Beginning of the Finale)